Title: Automatically Position Non-Overlapping Text Labels with
        'ggplot2'
Description: Provides text and label geoms for 'ggplot2' that help to avoid
    overlapping text labels. Labels repel away from each other and away from the
    data points.
Depends: R (>= 4.5.0), ggplot2 (>= 3.5.2)
Imports: grid, Rcpp, rlang (>= 1.1.6), S7, scales (>= 1.4.0), withr (>=
        3.0.2)
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, testthat, svglite, vdiffr, gridExtra, ggpp,
        patchwork, devtools, prettydoc, ggbeeswarm, dplyr, magrittr,
        readr, stringr, marquee, rsvg, sf
